               <msContents>
                  <summary>End of a lease of or labor contract for a vineyard; the financial arrangements are not completely clear, especially the nature of the 80 drachmas of lines 3-4 and the amount of the advance loan</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers: about half of the front contains writing; the back is blank; the papyrus is broken on the top and left and shows holes, tears, and wrinkles</note>
                     <note type="general">23 lines of writing by a ligatured inclined hand, which shows some features reminiscent of the chancery</note>
                     <note type="general">There are 7 panels of writing and it is likely that 3 more are missing</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">In Greek</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
